<title type="html"><![CDATA[8/1(Thu.) German gender pay gap unchanged at 21 percent/WHO slams electronic cigarettes, tobacco industy (Host:Danny)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=303&amp;p=319#p319"><![CDATA[
8/1(Thu.) German gender pay gap unchanged at 21 percent/UN health agency WHO slams electronic cigarettes, tobacco industry (Host:Danny)<br /><br />Session 1 :German gender pay gap unchanged at 21 percent<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.dw.com/en/german-gender-pay-gap-unchanged-at-21-percent/a-47906057">https://www.dw.com/en/german-gender-pay ... a-47906057</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br /><br />1. What do you feel after reading this news?<br />2. Some &quot;structural&quot; reasons in the article explains gender pay gap. Do you agree with the reasons mentioned in the article?<br />2. In Taiwan, do you think that there are differences between men and women in salary? Should we protest?<br /><br />Session 2:UN health agency WHO slams electronic cigarettes, tobacco industry<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.dw.com/en/un-health-agency-who-slams-electronic-cigarettes-tobacco-industry/a-49763792">https://www.dw.com/en/un-health-agency- ... a-49763792</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br /><br />1. After read the article, Does that change your thought?<br />2. Does anyone tell you e-cigarette is healthier than normal cigarettes ? /Or you are a smoker, do you know the harm of smoking?<br />3. How to persuade people not to smoke. Or as a smoker, how to persuade people around he/she smoke is not so serious.<br /><br /><br />Suggested Agenda<br />7:00 p.m. --7:30 p.m. free talk <br />7:30 p.m. --8:10 p.m. first topic discussion <br />8:10 p.m. --8:40 p.m. Presentation (All participants are invited)<br />8:40 p.m.-- 9.:15 p.m. second topic discussion <br />9:15 p.m.-- 9:30 p.m. Presentation<br /><br />speaker time : 2 minutes for each speaker<br />host time : 3 minutes<br /><br />The meeting place of Thursday:<br />丹堤咖啡寶慶店：台北市延平南路107號2F (上樓右邊第三區塊)<br />捷運資訊： 近台北捷運–西門站 (4號出口步行約2分鐘，康是美隔壁)<br />丹堤低消: NT$80元<br />最自由的全英文會話聚會,前三次不用交會費,加入會員終生會費NT$500，帶著開放與熱情來學英文<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Sat Jul 27, 2019 7:25 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
